SuspectedCovid19PatientsRegistryDataMart

SuspectedCovid19PatientsRegistryDataMart is loaded from DM_COVID_SUSPECTED and DM_COVID_SUSPECTED_EXT. DM_COVID_SUSPECTED and DM_COVID_SUSPECTED_EXT are Clarity data mart tables that store information related to the COVID-19 Suspected Registry metrics. Each row represents metric data for a patient for a specific timespan. Only patients that meet the inclusion criteria for the COVID-19 Suspected Registry have information stored in this table. This table stores the data from the latest Clarity extract only.

Properties

Reporting table name
dbo.SuspectedCovid19PatientsRegistryDataMart
Granularity
